{"tid":2142024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"強如3.3級地震 現巨型蘑菇雲  貝魯特大爆炸 毀30萬家園113死","createTime":"2020-08-06T06:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T10:02:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"6d5c39c45382faf516ca5b26fc4d8aa33b55cc16","tid":2142024,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:25:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200806/U5QEXVEMM77D6LQY73SYLPXUTQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200806%2FU5QEXVEMM77D6LQY73SYLPXUTQ%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOpzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=e2ca6563\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200806%2FU5QEXVEMM77D6LQY73SYLPXUTQ%2F&h=7bc36c3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200806/U5QEXVEMM77D6LQY73SYLPXUTQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n強如3.3級地震 現巨型蘑菇雲 <br />\n貝魯特大爆炸 毀30萬家園113死<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【驚世災劫】<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩首都貝魯特前日發生歷來威力最強的爆炸，現場出現巨型蘑菇雲，造成嚴重破壞，至少113人死逾4,000傷。爆炸疑與一個倉庫存放了六年的2,750公噸硝酸銨有關。全黎巴嫩昨日起哀悼三天。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EUCYomBKLc7rdMgvPygHFhaJeRo=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TNQZXDGEBFPLAAYAPRRGJFVJL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEUCYomBKLc7rdMgvPygHFhaJeRo%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTNQZXDGEBFPLAAYAPRRGJFVJL4.jpg&h=ac004653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從高空拍攝可見港口面目全非，貝魯特多處被夷為平地。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n貝魯特港口區在當地時間黃昏6時後未幾兩度爆炸，現場片段所見，事前先有火光，當地傳媒指起火的包括煙花倉庫；火勢蔓。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：如核爆煉獄 「我們被詛咒」<br />\n<br />\n隔海塞浦路斯感震動<br />\n<br />\n爆炸威力相等於黎克特制3.3級地震，港口一帶事後滿目瘡痍，市中。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n事後受訪一度激動落淚的貝魯特省長阿布德指，爆炸毀掉逾半個貝魯特市，損失多達50億美元（390億港元），多達30萬人無家可歸。總統奧恩建議貝魯特進入緊急狀態兩周，另設1,000億黎巴嫩鎊（5.1億港元）應急基金，貝魯特將進入兩周緊急狀態。<br />\n<br />\n爆炸死傷者不乏外國人，一名澳洲公民喪生，荷蘭大使館五人傷，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n事後有數百人失蹤，可能被困瓦礫，但當局指停電增加夜間搜救難度，雖。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0bjr2ogNmCwOag7NUJBGmWqNlP0=/190x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CSPBGLMQCDKOSJJLDNJ3PMX7WQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0bjr2ogNmCwOag7NUJBGmWqNlP0%3D%2F190x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCSPBGLMQCDKOSJJLDNJ3PMX7WQ.gif&h=70071a61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爆炸威力強大，現場出現巨型蘑菇雲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疑焊接引爆存倉硝酸銨<br />\n<br />\n內政部長法赫米指，懷疑涉事的倉庫位於碼頭，存放的硝酸銨2014年從一。。。。。。。。。<br />\n。。。。。。。以貪腐聞名，更跟其他公共機構一樣，被各政治派系包括真主黨操控。<br />\n<br />\n總理迪亞卜在電視演說稱「我們正目睹真正災難」，又承諾追究肇事者責任。消息指當局軟禁了2014年以來負責該倉庫儲存及保安的官員。<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩深陷經濟危機，加上近期日趨嚴峻的武漢肺炎疫情，爆炸只會令當地醫。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。損毀嚴重，有聲稱是該院醫生者指16名醫護人員及病人在爆炸中死亡。<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩政局一向不穩，恐襲、轟炸頻仍，加上明天。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。觸動真主黨支持者神經，爆炸一度被懷疑為襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n外界亦擔心必需品幾乎全部入口的黎巴嫩，民眾如何在主要港口受損下生存。估計全國85%小麥，都存放在已炸到不成形的港口穀倉，高官更指穀倉所有小麥都被污染，不可食用，該國糧食儲備不足一個月。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/路透社/法新社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WUjALun4H-r1rOozUd-JBJvGPCI=/190x132/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JSMCX6FF5WZAQEW37YCJYG3YPI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWUjALun4H-r1rOozUd-JBJvGPCI%3D%2F190x132%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJSMCX6FF5WZAQEW37YCJYG3YPI.gif&h=c408ca08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9671c9e5b2d0d15a484c5c670201239ebb71ade","tid":2142024,"uid":214502,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:27:00.000Z","msg":"85%小麥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72647285d0416c627ae01aa84903d352c444b908","tid":2142024,"uid":78243,"